### 获取文章列表

POST {{host}}/api/blog/query

### 创建文章, 更新文章

POST {{host}}/api/blog/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "标题",
    "category_code": "default",
    "summary": "摘要",
    "content_rich": "正文",
    "tags": ["aa", "bb"]
}


### 更新文章

PUT {{host}}/api/blog/detail/1

{
    "title": "标题111",
    "summary": null
}

### 获取文章详情

GET {{host}}/api/blog/detail/1


### 删除文章

DELETE {{host}}/api/blog/detail/1


